  "detailed_description": "As a rookie female soldier being lost memory. Your are tasked with investigating a group of criminals in the deserted city of Orland and unknowingly discovering a secret ruins underground.<br>And here, you being attacked and chased by demons, things drag on after things ... the true origin of the world gradually reveal... and then, as \"The Chosen One\" - you have to protect the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Top-down shoot em up and hack and slash gameplay<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195020/extras/2ef605f54f7ac23333c38b779fbd33c5.poster.avif?t=1726100661\" width=400 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195020/extras/2ef605f54f7ac23333c38b779fbd33c5.webm?t=1726100661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195020/extras/2ef605f54f7ac23333c38b779fbd33c5.mp4?t=1726100661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195020/extras/ae6324ac1a126d932e48703a631b3728.poster.avif?t=1726100661\" width=400 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195020/extras/ae6324ac1a126d932e48703a631b3728.webm?t=1726100661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195020/extras/ae6324ac1a126d932e48703a631b3728.mp4?t=1726100661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Fun and challenge boss fighting<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195020/extras/5eb7528ad